🌿 EcoSwap Marketplace
EcoSwap is a Flask-based web application that enables users to exchange products through a swap system.

🚀 Features
User Registration & Login (Password Hashing Enabled)
Add Products
View Marketplace
Send Swap Requests
Accept / Reject Swap Requests
Product Removal after Successful Swap
Bootstrap UI Design
🛠 Tech Stack
Python
Flask
SQLite
HTML & Bootstrap
Jinja2 Templates
⚙ Installation Guide
Clone the repository
Install dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
Run the application: python app.py
Open in browser: http://127.0.0.1:5000
